Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not anyone asked for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will all be participating\Nin internships with pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got an offer from a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero's name is Gran Torino.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a teacher at U.A. for only one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who was my homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here from U.A. High.\NMy name is Izuku Midoriya...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet yo--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was carrying a string of sausages\Nwith ketchup poured over them, I fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:20.20,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Gran Torino"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.78,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Izuku Midoriya - Quirk: One For All"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too easily misunderstood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Izuku Midoriya from U.A.!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Izuku Midoriya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's All Might's teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he would be pretty old, but this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshinori!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'm going to make a phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:03:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I should let All Might\Nknow about the state this guy's in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire off a One For All at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know how well you can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy? Suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good costume. Wear it and fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and quickly become able to handle my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because All Might doesn't have any time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't waste time messing around with you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, there's even\Nmore reason to fire one off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You zygote!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bizarre! Gran Torino Appears"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched the U.A. sports festival on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you used that power was unthinkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's called the symbol of peace\Nand the number one hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that justice-obsessed All Might is\Nworse than a novice when it comes to teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we begin, you zygotes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using the same phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way they play dumb is the same, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person must be\NAll Might's teacher, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand watching\Nhow you're using your power,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, put on your costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.48,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hero Costume β for Mr. Izuku Midoriya"\N"Specifications & User Manual"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The user manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Mr. Izuku Midoriya,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when making repairs to your costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our company decided to make\Nsome changes to the materials and design.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it'll definitely\Nbe a lot cooler like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They changed the materials\Nand design without asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if everyone in the\Nsupport business is like Hatsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it's my first battle\Nwith version β of my mom's suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't know\Nhow well I can use this suit yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if there isn't more space,\Nif I fire at 100% by accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your body wouldn't be able to take it, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, you're such a chatterbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing patience!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having real combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't see my true\Nstrength with that hit earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the ninth holder of\NOne For All is such a wet blanket...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Might is a real novice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his Quirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under these circumstances where\Nthere's no place to hide and no openings,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than carefully figuring out where he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should keep him from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine the egg not\Nbreaking inside the microwave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's passed behind me twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Analysis and prediction, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's discord within your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it turned out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you used One For All in\Nthe cavalry battle and the tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should already understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your admiration for All Might\Nand your sense of duty are like shackles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shackles"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that you need to get stronger, fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But time and enemies won't\Nwait until you get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking One For All\Nis more special than it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about the answer yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy some grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the cleaning to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My admiration for All Might... is a shackle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:52.11,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Same Time - Hosu City"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, we're mostly just\Nwaiting for calls from clients,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but recently, you know,\NHosu's been kind of hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:08:00.12,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Manual"\N"Tenya Iida - Quirk: Engine"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Street patrols become a way to suppress crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, I can't believe Ingenium's\Nlittle brother is interning at my agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you had offers from\Nheroes more capable than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Killer... So elusive, he can't even\Nbe caught by the net of modern society.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this might be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I cannot {\i1}not{\i0} go after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... cannot forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.95,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Villain - Tomura Shigaraki - Quirk: Decay"\N"Villain - Kurogiri - Quirk: Warp Gate"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the ones who attacked U.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you want to add me to your numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:51.21,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Villain - Stain"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Come on, you've got so\Nmuch more experience as a villain, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I just want to kill All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to break everything I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kids like this, too... Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was foolish to be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the type of person I hate the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to go along\Nwith your childish tantrum?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What meaning is there\Nin killing without conviction?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Killer: Stain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man brought in to spur
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomura Shigaraki's growth, since he cares only about destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, is it all right to let this continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point if we just tell him the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should think about\Nwhere he still needs to mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spur on his growth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what it means to educate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My admiration for All Might is a shackle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I understand how to use it,\Nthere's discord in my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking One For All\Nis more special than it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what's making my movements stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "stiff" mean in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it another way,\Nwhat makes movement flexible?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flexible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.38,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hero Analysis for the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about One For All\Nand the smash as a special move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it used up close--why didn't I notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Quirks are part of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to think of\NOne For All more, more evenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His thinking is flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that from the way\Nhe moved at the sports festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found someone pretty good, huh, Toshinori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Might...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.87,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Izuku Midoriya"\N"Quirk: One For All"\N"Smashes villains with a super power passed down from one generation to the next."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.87,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}"Affiliation: U.A. High School Hero Class 1-A"\N"Birthday: 7/15"\N"Height: 166 cm" "Blood Type: O" "Likes: Pork Cutlet Bowls"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:54.88,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gran Torino"\N"Quirk: Jet"\N"He can move freely in the air with jet propulsion using the air that comes out of the soles of his feet."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:54.88,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}"Affiliation: Pro Hero"\N"Birthday: 1/28"\N"Height: 120 cm" "Blood Type: B" "Likes: {\i1}Taiyaki{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In the center of Tokyo"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only chose my agency because
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:11.48,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No. 4 Hero – Best Jeanist"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the top five\Nmost popular heroes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:14.44,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Katsuki Bakugo - Quirk: Explosion"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that put in an offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I've only been\Ngetting good little kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you were the first one\Nin a while to strike a chord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched you at the sports festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to freely manipulate\Na Quirk with high potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and had a good grasp of application as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an outstanding talent already\Ngood enough to recruit as a sidekick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you have a fatal flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe yourself to be the strongest,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you try to put that into practice\Nnot caring about how that looks--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a ferocious nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you choose me to give me a lecture--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is part of my work as a\Nhero to correct people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes and villains are\Ntwo sides of the same coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show those glaring eyes of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what makes someone a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm educating you to become an exemplary hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you speak, your appearance,\Ncontrolling your emotions, enforcing your morals...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are countless things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the short period of a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will sew all that into your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.31,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fourth Kind Agency"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:34.31,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tetsutetsu Tetsutetsu - Quirk: Steel"\N"Eijiro Kirishima - Quirk: Hardening"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsutetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:39.27,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chivalrous Hero: Fourth Kind"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to put two offers in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started without ado.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw your guts at the sports festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, being a hero's not so easy\Nthat you can rely on brute force alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will teach you that as someone\Nwith more experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of the Chivalrous Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me to finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you manners properly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll tell you the major premise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pro heroes receive wages from\Nthe government, so we are civil servants,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but because of how this came about,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,civil servants and\Npro heroes are very different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the actual duties of a pro hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basic hero duties involve\Ncontrolling crime, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:30.45,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle Hero: Gunhead"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a crime occurs,\Nthe police will contact heroes for support.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The requests will come\Nall at once by district, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We file reports on the services we provided,\Nlike assisting with arrests or rescuing people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the government office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we receive pay based on an\Nexamination conducted by a special agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We usually get a percentage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.71,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ochaco Uraraka - Quirk: Zero Gravity"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he talks is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.97,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"TV Station"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, heroes are\Nallowed to have side jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this was made official,\Nthere was a lot of argument about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:55.31,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Snake Hero: Uwabami"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that ended thanks to\Nour popularity and public demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now, I'm about to film a commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick around, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.57,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Itsuka Kendo - Quirk: Big Fist"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to experience\Nsomething more hero-like, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is not something you can\Navoid if you want to become a pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.40,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Momo Yaoyorozu - Quirk: Creation"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, she is the one\Nwho fell for pathetic little me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will learn as much as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going all out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all we can do while\Nyou're filming is watch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why I chose you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because you fell\Nfor our qualifications as heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also because you're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.44,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tatooin Station"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes must practice and train every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:45.32,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kyoka Jiro - Quirk: Earphone Jack"\N"Pro Hero - Death Arms"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't change even if they are on patrol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is harder than class!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An important part of being a hero\Nis knowing how to pass idle hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:54.54,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Mt. Lady - Quirk: Gigantification"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:00.46,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Minoru Mineta - Quirk: Pop Off"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not into this kind of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.80,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tsuyu Asui - Quirk: Frog"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for you, Shoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you are finally ready\Nto take the path of the mighty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of\Ngoing down a path you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.22,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shoto Todoroki - Quirk: Half-Cold, Half-Hot"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, you should get ready, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.60,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Endeavor - Quirk: Hellflame"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what a hero is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Internship Day 1 - Night"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z! Z!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He {\i1}is{\i0} sleeping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first day, he ended up just testing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't do any hero work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after coming back from\Nbuying food, he went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gran Torino. I didn't get any hits\Nwhen I searched his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A U.A. teacher for just one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of mysteries about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to think of One For All,\Nof my own Quirk, more evenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Kacchan and the others can\Ndo as naturally as breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel the need to\N"use" in a conscious way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can use my power at 5% like breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,movements like that won't be impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Aizawa and Kirishima said so, too--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can master my Quirk,\Nthere's a lot I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, using it\Ninstantaneously and intermittently!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's a matter of getting used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with just 5%,\NI should be able to cross this distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can go jump, jump, jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it'd be really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine an egg not breaking in the microwave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I knew this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to brace myself... and cushion my arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, from the second jump,\NI'll need to put power into my arms and legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.62,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Snap"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I don't do it quickly,\Nthen I might break more bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.63,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thud"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take too long to\Nvisualize like I usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforce my arms--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch faster--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! We shouldn't get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was training on my own yesterday\Nand got a little too caught up in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to digest what you said\Nto me and put it into practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your first time trying it,\Nso that's only to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to get that kind\Nof thinking from All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he was able to use\Nit normally from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I taught him in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His only redeeming feature was his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Might as a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was he like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing but practical training for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he was so scared of you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't teach him half-heartedly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he was the man entrusted to me\Nby my sworn friend, who had passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? All Might's predecessor passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't told him about\Nthe seventh holder, Toshinori?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A microwave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, it broke yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I used expedited delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell if he's serious or faking it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, kid! We're gonna eat those\Nfrozen {\i1}taiyaki{\i0} I bought yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having {\i1}taiyaki{\i0} for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To use One For All like I'm breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it objectively,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to catch up to the feeling\Neveryone else had fifteen years to cultivate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time waits for no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, in order to\Ndraw out more than 5% of my power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need as long as it'd\Ntake to build up my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is it! Get it while it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My time is limited...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, just eat a piping hot {\i1}taiyaki{\i0} and--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I microwaved it on defrost, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?\NYou stuck a huge plate in, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you force a plate\Nin like that, it won't turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so only part of it will get hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first time using a microwave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.48,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Growl"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ours wasn't the turning type...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorr--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gran Torino!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This {\i1}taiyaki{\i0} is... me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, I've insisted\Non "using" One For All.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using it when I need it,\Nin the places that need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like flipping on a switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with that, my reaction time got slower\Nand slower with the second and third moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then I should've turned\Nthe switch on throughout from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagining the heat that used\Nto only be in one place...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...spreading throughout my whole body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't take him long to figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my whole body, continuously!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the upper limit of\Nwhat my body will allow--5%!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To visualize a {\i1}taiyaki{\i0} in a microwave\Nis really boring. You okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Might's already said... that's fine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you move in that state?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't... know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:21.88,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally called me for the preview, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tomura Shigaraki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took a long time, don't you think, Midoriya?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything to do with--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, starting this week,\NI'll be in charge of all the previews.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! All Might!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Midoriya and Shigaraki."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The League of Villains goes wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush all of you,\Nwhether you're a hero, or a hero killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:51.41,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Midoriya and Shigaraki"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go.
